flowchart LR
  subgraph CH[User Channels]
    A1[Call Center Agent Desktop\nReact Web]
    A2[Member Portal\nWeb and Mobile]
    A3[Supervisor and QA Console]
    A4[SMS and IVR Bot\noptional]
  end

  subgraph APP[App and Orchestration Layer]
    B1[API Gateway and WAF\nOAuth2 OIDC, rate limits]
    B2[Assistant Orchestrator\nintent and tool routing]
    B3[Conversation Service\nstate and memory policy]
    B4[Prompt and Policy Service\nSystem prompts and templates]
    B5[Structured Context Library SCL\ncurated schemas, definitions, guardrails]
  end

  subgraph AI[Model and Retrieval Layer]
    C1[LLM Inference\non prem or private endpoint]
    C2[RAG Retrieval Service]
    C3[Vector DB\nembeddings for docs, transcripts, FAQs]
    C4[Embedding Service]
    C5[Rules and Deterministic Engines\nbenefit calc and code mapping]
  end

  subgraph DATA[Enterprise Data and Systems]
    D1[Member and Eligibility SoR\ncore admin and MDM]
    D2[Benefits Plan Config\nproduct and benefits]
    D3[Claims Platform\nEDI 835 837 and adjudication]
    D4[Prior Auth Platform]
    D5[CRM and Case Management\nSalesforce Dynamics etc]
    D6[Doc Repositories\nSharePoint Confluence file shares]
    D7[Call Recordings and CCaaS]
    D8[Cloud Data Platform and Lakehouse]
  end

  subgraph GOV[Security, Compliance, Monitoring]
    E1[Audit Logging PHI safe\nrequest and response traces]
    E2[Evaluation and Quality Gates\nfactuality tone citations]
    E3[PHI and PII Controls\nDLP redaction encryption]
    E4[Model Risk Management\nCMS and HIPAA policy checks]
    E5[Feature Store and Metrics\nAHT FCR CSAT deflection]
  end

